metadata.editComments: I really adore the rarity of the chords in this song, even without having understood the lyrics at first (I'm Spanish speaker). It sounds like it was made in negative harmony (full of inverted chords hehe). Although any modification in the notes and/or chords are welcome.
Reverted to the previous omitted chords. There are no natural chords here. In the first measure there's a notable addition of 2nd/9th, and in measure 8 there's also a slight inversion of D with F#º.
